== HiDPI displays ==
If text and other UI elements appear tiny on your [[wikipedia:HiDPI|HiDPI]] display, then check the following:

* [[Troubleshooting#Checking_the_Java_version|Double check that you are running the 64-bit version of Java]].
* Verify that you are running Windows 10 (Windows 7 and 8 do not do HiDPI scaling).
* In {{bc|ImageJ.exe|Properties|Compatibility}}, ensure that the "Disable display scaling on high DPI settings" option is ''not'' enabled.

